 * - Classes: `.className`  `{ class: 'className' }`
 * - IDs: `#myId`  `{ id: 'myId' }`
 * - Key-value pairs: `key="value"`  `{ key: 'value' }`
 * - Boolean attributes: `disabled`  `{ disabled: true }`
 *
 * @param attrString - The attribute string to parse
